---
  layout: layouts/base.njk
  title: Blog of Rafael Calvo
  header: 'Blog posts'
  description: 'Here I write about various things, including web design and development, how I did some things, some tutorials and more.'
  images: https://i.ibb.co/JBCcQh6/Blog-Card-en.png
---

<header class="blog-header">
  <h1>{{ header }}</h1>
  <p>{{ description }}</p>
</header>

<ul class="posts-list">
  {%- for post in collections.blog_en | reverse -%}
  <li class="post">
    <h3>
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    </h3>
    <span class="post-date"
      ><strong>{{ post.date | readableDate }}</strong></span
    >
    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    <a class="read-more" href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ 'read_more' | i18n }} â†’</a>
  </li>
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>
